cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.DL. 

The paper deals with knowledge base completion and entity discovery, which are topics related to databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of tables on the web and the need to match them to elements of a KB suggest a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the use of machine learning techniques for entity discovery points to deep learning (cs.DL) as a possible sub-category.
